text: Gwynedd Ethnicity 99.0% White Politics MPs * Guto Bebb * Elfyn Llwyd * Hywel Williams AMs * Dafydd Elis-Thomas * Gareth Jones * Alun Ffred Jones * North Wales * Mid and West Wales MEPs * Wales Gwynedd is a large area in North West Wales. It has a long coast-line with many cliffs and beaches. It also has many mountains including Snowdon, the highest mountain in England and Wales. Large towns include Bangor and Caernarfon. The county was divided into five districts: Aberconwy, Arfon, Dwyfor, Meirionnydd and Anglesey.
title: Gwynedd
